            <title>[FELIX-1930] Clicking action on bundles detail page shows full bundle list while URL stays on bundles/&lt;id&gt;</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-1930</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1. Go to webconsole, click on a bundle to go to its detail page (eg. /system/bundles/1)&lt;br/&gt;
2. Click on any action (stop/start/uninstall etc.)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Problem:&lt;br/&gt;
=&amp;gt; The content of the page will switch to the list of all bundles (like /system/bundles) but the URL stays on /system/bundles/1&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Expected:&lt;br/&gt;
=&amp;gt; Only the bundle detail content is refreshed (reflecting the status change from the action), URL stays on /system/bundles/1&lt;/p&gt;</description>
